review_blob: Crisp apples, beautiful pale blonde with a luxurious head...  A bit of champagne feel to the carbonation...  Overall very great saison... Would of liked a bit more spice but good enough for a great beer... I mean thats just me after 13 hours of work... cheers...
Caramel and alcohol apparent to taste, nice carbonation and constant lacing. Bit cloudy but doesnt matter .  Great taste fruity malty caramel tones. Great beer.
Amazing mouthfeel and aroma. Love taste of malty sweey goodness and slight fruitiness...

Great beer but have had more impressive doubles ipa. Has a great taste and mouthfeel. Love the lingering biterness no head retention although my server does not know how to pour a sprite from a good beer
Great session beer, amazing aroma obviously dry hopped. Great mouthfeel and pleasing lingering aftertaste.
